428
00:35:01,319 --> 00:35:05,819
泣かないよ 昔君と見た きれいな空だったから
I won't cry, because it was a beautiful sky I saw with you long ago

429
00:35:15,619 --> 00:35:24,319
あの道まで 響く靴の音が耳に残る
Along that road, the echoing sound of shoes remains in my ears

430
00:35:25,319 --> 00:35:34,319
大きな自分の影を見つめて 想うのでしょう
Staring at my own large shadow, I wonder what I'm thinking

431
00:35:34,819 --> 00:35:39,519
ちっとも変わらないはずなのに
Even though it shouldn't have changed at all

432
00:35:39,819 --> 00:35:44,319
せつない気持ちふくらんでく
These painful feelings keep swelling up

433
00:35:44,619 --> 00:35:52,319
どんなに想ったって 君はもういない
No matter how much I miss you, you're already gone

434
00:35:53,819 --> 00:36:02,619
行きたいよ 君のそばに 小さくても小さくても
I want to go to your side, even if it's small, even if it's small

435
00:36:03,319 --> 00:36:12,719
1番に君が好きだよ 強くいられる
I love you the most, I can be strong

436
00:36:13,319 --> 00:36:22,319
願いを流れ星に そっと唱えてみたけれど
I whispered a wish to a shooting star, but...

437
00:36:22,619 --> 00:36:32,319
泣かないよ 届くだろう きれいな空に
I won't cry, it will reach that beautiful sky

438
00:36:49,819 --> 00:36:54,319
会えなくても 記憶をたどって
Even if we can't meet, I'll trace my memories

439
00:36:54,319 --> 00:36:59,619
同じ幸せを見たいんだ
I want to see the same happiness

440
00:36:59,819 --> 00:37:08,319
あの香りとともに 花火がぱっと開く
Along with that scent, fireworks burst open

441
00:37:08,819 --> 00:37:17,819
行きたいよ 君のところへ 小さな手をにぎりしめて
I want to go to you, clutching our small hands

442
00:37:18,319 --> 00:37:27,319
泣きたいよ それはそれは きれいな空だった
I want to cry, it was, oh it was, a beautiful sky

443
00:37:28,319 --> 00:37:36,319
願いを流れ星に そっと唱えてみたけれど
I whispered a wish to a shooting star, but...

444
00:37:36,619 --> 00:37:47,319
泣きたいよ 届かない想いをこの空に...
I want to cry, my unreachable feelings into this sky...

445
00:38:33,319 --> 00:38:38,319
[曲：RELAY / 作詞：カトウチヒロ / 作曲：Konami Amusement]
[Song: RELAY / Lyrics: Chihiro Kato / Composition: Konami Amusement]

446
00:39:05,319 --> 00:39:10,319
もっ何十回 もう何百回も 震えるソラ見上げて
Dozens of times, hundreds of times, looking up at the trembling sky

447
00:39:10,319 --> 00:39:14,819
辿り着いた場所が 運命のダイヤモンド
The place we arrived at is the diamond of destiny

448
00:39:14,819 --> 00:39:20,819
何千回 もう何万回も 涙流したきみへ
To you who shed tears thousands, tens of thousands of times

449
00:39:20,819 --> 00:39:24,819
ねえ 諦められたことはあったっけ？
Tell me, was there ever anything we could just give up on?

450
00:39:25,319 --> 00:39:30,319
「憧れ＝限界」だから もういらないよ
Because "aspiration = limit", I don't need it anymore

451
00:39:30,319 --> 00:39:35,819
そこにとどまるなんて もったいないでしょ
Just staying there is such a waste, right?

452
00:39:35,819 --> 00:39:45,819
それぞれの物語 交差する瞬間を 見つめる意味は
The meaning of watching the moment our respective stories intersect is...

453
00:39:47,819 --> 00:39:52,819
放った夢だけ 大きな弧を描いて
Only the dreams we let go of draw a big arc

454
00:39:52,819 --> 00:39:56,819
はちきれそうな煌めきを
Carrying a sparkle that's about to burst

455
00:39:56,819 --> 00:40:01,319
消えることなく どこまででも
Without fading away, wherever it may go

456
00:40:02,179 --> 00:40:03,479
世界の向こうに
To the other side of the world...

457
