届けよう
...let's deliver it!

458
00:40:05,379 --> 00:40:07,579
終わることのない
Never-ending...

459
00:40:07,579 --> 00:40:10,579
この胸 of 衝動は
...this impulse in my heart...

460
00:40:10,579 --> 00:40:11,779
どうしたって
...no matter what...

461
00:40:11,779 --> 00:40:13,379
どうしても
...no matter how...

462
00:40:13,379 --> 00:40:15,479
ぼくを呼んでいた
...was calling out to me.

463
00:40:15,479 --> 00:40:16,479
だから
That's why...

464
00:40:16,479 --> 00:40:18,579
その先へと
...to the future beyond...

465
00:40:18,579 --> 00:40:21,579
走り続ける
...I will keep running.

466
00:40:21,579 --> 00:40:25,579
次へ 次へ
To the next, to the next!

467
00:41:04,479 --> 00:41:07,079
妄想だった 中途半端な
It was just a delusion, a half-hearted...

468
00:41:07,079 --> 00:41:09,579
ふがいなさ 抱えて
...helplessness that I carried...

469
00:41:09,579 --> 00:41:12,179
立ち尽くしていた 通り雨
...as I stood frozen in the rain.

470
00:41:12,179 --> 00:41:14,879
通り雨はプレリュード
The passing rain is a prelude.

471
00:41:15,079 --> 00:41:17,679
何千回も 何万回も
Thousands of times, tens of thousands of times...

472
00:41:17,679 --> 00:41:20,279
挑み続けた きみへ
...to you, who kept on challenging.

473
