ねえ 聴かせてよ「夢は叶うんだ」って
Hey, let me hear you say, "dreams do come true!"

474
00:41:25,179 --> 00:41:30,179
「諦め＝完敗」ならば 絶対にないよ
If "giving up = complete defeat," then that's absolutely not happening.

475
00:41:30,179 --> 00:41:33,079
だれに邪魔されようと
No matter who tries to get in our way...

476
00:41:33,079 --> 00:41:35,579
ためらわないで
...don't hesitate!

477
00:41:35,579 --> 00:41:38,079
託された情熱を
The passion entrusted to us...

478
00:41:38,079 --> 00:41:41,279
落とさずに つないでく
...we will pass it on without letting it drop.

479
00:41:41,279 --> 00:41:44,979
そう 最後まで
Yes, until the very end!

480
00:41:47,779 --> 00:41:50,479
フラグに誓い
Swearing on the flag...

481
00:41:50,479 --> 00:41:52,479
雄々しく はためいて
...letting it flutter bravely...

482
00:41:52,479 --> 00:41:55,479
鳴り止まない ファンファーレ
...an endless fanfare...

483
00:41:55,479 --> 00:41:57,479
いつも心に
...was always...

484
00:41:57,479 --> 00:42:01,479
流れていた
...flowing in my heart.

485
00:42:01,479 --> 00:42:05,479
遠い未来へ 祈るよう
As if praying to a distant future...

486
00:42:05,479 --> 00:42:07,279
忘れられない
...I cannot forget...

487
00:42:07,279 --> 00:42:09,579
あの日々の後悔を
...the regrets of those days.

488
00:42:09,579 --> 00:42:10,879
追いかけて 追いかけて
Chasing after them, chasing after them...

489
00:42:10,879 --> 00:42:13,579
滑り込んだ
...I slipped into...

490
00:42:13,579 --> 00:42:16,479
この想い
...these feelings.

491
00:42:16,479 --> 00:42:18,679
青いソラに
Into the blue sky...

492
00:42:18,679 --> 00:42:21,579
ふと 溢れていった
...they suddenly overflowed...

493
00:42:21,579 --> 00:42:26,979
遠く 遠く
...far, far away.

494
00:42:53,679 --> 00:42:55,179
終わらない 終わらない
It's never-ending, never-ending!

495
00:42:55,179 --> 00:42:57,279
仕事が山積み 終わらない
A mountain of work, it's never-ending!

496
00:42:57,279 --> 00:42:59,279
止まらない 止まらない
It's unstoppable, unstoppable!

497
00:42:59,279 --> 00:43:01,179
それでも時間は 止まらない
But still, time won't stop!

498
00:43:01,179 --> 00:43:02,179
YO! YO!

499
00:43:02,179 --> 00:43:03,479
ヘッド ヘット
Weary, exhausted,

500
00:43:03,479 --> 00:43:04,279
溜まり溜まった ヘント
with so much pent-up resentment.

501
00:43:04,279 --> 00:43:05,279
天罰 唱えろ バット
Invoke divine punishment, bat!

502
00:43:05,279 --> 00:43:06,279
コンボ 滅する 金属バット
Destructive combo with a metal bat!

503
00:43:06,279 --> 00:43:07,279
Swing!

504
00:43:08,279 --> 00:43:09,279
今日もてんこ盛り
Today is packed full too,

505
00:43:09,279 --> 00:43:10,279
今日もてんこ盛り
today is packed full too!

506
00:43:10,279 --> 00:43:11,279
Wah!

507
00:43:11,279 --> 00:43:12,679
No more 無知
No more ignorance!

508
00:43:13,179 --> 00:43:14,679
ギミギミ じゅし
Gimme, gimme juicy!

509
00:43:14,679 --> 00:43:15,379
I see

510
00:43:15,379 --> 00:43:16,879
奔走 Anytime 奔走 Anytime
Running around anytime, running around anytime!

511
00:43:17,679 --> 00:43:18,779
はぁーあ
*Sigh*

512
00:43:19,079 --> 00:43:20,179
骨抜き ぶれすで
Weak-kneed breath...

513
00:43:20,179 --> 00:43:21,479
N3 すからぱん
N3, empty-pocketed...

514
00:43:21,479 --> 00:43:22,279
わっしょい
Wasshoi!

515
00:43:22,479 --> 00:43:24,679
自分自身に 厳しすぎちゃう
Too hard on myself,

516
00:43:24,679 --> 00:43:26,579
すぐさま ヘラヘラ 優等生
instantly smiling, the honor student,

517
00:43:26,579 --> 00:43:28,679
さっぱり足らない 順応性
with absolutely no adaptability.

518
00:43:29,279 --> 00:43:32,079
自分自身としっかり 向き合う
Facing myself properly,

519
00:43:32,279 --> 00:43:35,879
一番 必要なものは トレビアン
the most necessary thing is très bien.

520
00:43:36,379 --> 00:43:39,279
ご褒美を頂戴
